    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model predicts RH within ±12% of experimental values across all 5 operating points, satisfying the ±15% acceptance criterion. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 given the medium model influence and documented justifications. The assessment team concludes the model is sufficiently credible to support the worst-case hemolysis identification decision for the Class II CPB device.",
